Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,...e a fábrica de Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Apaguem o fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Detenham todos que perderem o controle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Enquanto a batalha continuar,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,o número de vítimas \Ncontinuará aumentando.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,V-Viola...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Quantos oficiais da Família\N Donquixote ainda estão de pé?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:15.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda restam muitos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Na fábrica de Smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,uma das zonas de batalha, \Nhá um oficial protegendo-a:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.87,Main,,0,0,0,,o homem que pode nadar sobre\N qualquer superfície, Senhor Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:24.25,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(713.429,408.143)\blur0.9\fs50\fade(400,400)\c&H343131&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&}Fábrica de Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Na segunda zona, na estátua de pedra de Pica, está o oficial supremo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.39,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\pos(387.26,371.49)\blur0.9\fs50\fade(400,0)\c&H343131&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&}Estátua de Pica
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,o homem que se funde com a pedra, Pica!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,E na terceira zona, \No platô do Palácio Real,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,no andar superior estão...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,...o atual rei de Dressrosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,o homem de fios, Doflamingo;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,e seu chefe de gabinete, \No homem de muco, Trébol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,No campo de girassóis do quarto nível,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.53,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\move(184,209,-129,129,1,1128)\blur0.9\fs47\fade(0,0)\c&H343131&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&}Palácio Real
