Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:29.18,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\move(24.286,248.143,309.286,248.143,28,3656)\blur0.6\fs31\fade(0,0)\c&H343131&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&}Nível 2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Há quatro oficiais no segundo nível.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:33.62,Main,,0,0,0,,O meio-gyojin de peixe de luta, Dellinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.25,Main,,0,0,0,,O usuário do Jio-ken,{revisar}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Lao G!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,O humano com superpeso,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Machvise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,E a humana com o corpo inteiro armado,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda há dez com patente\N igual ou superior a oficial...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa brisa machuca meus olhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, que dureza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:37.11,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Oh, que dureza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Em muitas das batalhas...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,...já estão todos gravemente feridos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,O fim da batalha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,...não está muito longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:05.09,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,485)\fad(818,0)}PLANALTO DO PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:05.09,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(818,0)}QUARTO NÍVEL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Que insolente...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Army Bandera!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,O chão...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Que tal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora o chão ondula como uma bandeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece difícil ficar de pé aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Rebecca...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sei como você se sente!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe este lugar comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Galo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, depressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Perna Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Céus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Que sonolência me dá seu jeito de atacar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Prepare-se, Gladius!
